  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "Osprey's tidal rhythm bleeds into Onset's drum blend ratios, synchronizing the percussion architecture to the shoreline's own pulse. The wave period sets the kick's internal timing reference; the sea state determines how much the drum texture swells and recedes. Nature as the drum machine.",
